rvice! From world famous fish dip&nbsp;to fresh fish delivered daily, it's our pleasure to provide you with only the best quality products and experience. &nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div data-ux="GridCell" class="x-el x-el-div c1-1 c1-2 c1-8g c1-o c1-8p c1-8q c1-2y c1-34 c1-8r c1-5b c1-8s c1-b c1-c c1-a4 c1-a5 c1-8t c1-8u c1-8v c1-8w c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><div data-ux="ContentCard" index="1" id="e396ef00-2390-4d70-a376-42cf518de7cc" class="x-el x-el-div x-el c1-1 c1-2 c1-n c1-p c1-s c1-q c1-74 c1-r c1-4 c1-8x c1-8y c1-8z c1-b c1-c c1-90 c1-91 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g c1-1 c1-2 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><div data-ux="ContentCardWrapperImage" class="x-el x-el-div c1-1 c1-2 c1-2e c1-39 c1-3a c1-74 c1-4 c1-92 c1-93 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><picture data-lazyimg="true" class="x-el x-el-picture c1-1 c1-2 c1-4 c1-5t c1-74 c1-94 c1-26 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><source media="(max-width: 450px)" srcset="https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg/:/cr=t:12.5%25,l:0%25,w:100%25,h:75%25/rs=w:403,h:202,cg:true, //img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg/:/cr=t:12.5%25,  isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg 3x"/><source media="(min-width: 451px)" srcset="https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg/:/cr=t:12.5%25,l:0%25,w:100%25,h:75%25/rs=w:600,h:300,cg:true, //img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg/:/cr=t:12.5%25,  isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg 3x"/><img data-ux="Image" src="isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/0c35e61f-24c6-4dba-81a9-f6012c208e5c.jpg" data-aid="ABOUT_IMAGE_RENDERED1" class="x-el x-el-img c1-1 c1-2 c1-4 c1-2y c1-39 c1-3a c1-22 c1-24 c1-3b c1-95 c1-b c1-c c1-96 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"/></picture></div><h4 role="heading" aria-level="4" data-ux="ContentCardHeading" data-aid="ABOUT_HEADLINE_RENDERED1" data-typography="HeadingDelta" class="x-el x-el-h4 c1-1 c1-2 c1-2r c1-2a c1-97 c1-25 c1-23 c1-22 c1-24 c1-b c1-40 c1-6n c1-55 c1-6q c1-6s c1-6t c1-6u">27 years of customer satisfaction and quality</h4><div data-ux="ContentCardText" data-aid="ABOUT_DESCRIPTION_RENDERED1" data-typography="BodyAlpha" class="x-el c1-1 c1-2 c1-2r c1-2a c1-5p c1-22 c1-24 c1-7d c1-98 c1-99 c1-9a c1-9b c1-9c c1-9d c1-9e c1-9f c1-9g c1-9h c1-9i c1-9j c1-9k c1-9l c1-9m c1-9n c1-9o c1-9p c1-9q c1-9r c1-9s c1-9t c1-9u c1-9v c1-9w c1-9x c1-9y c1-9z c1-a0 c1-a1 c1-a2 c1-a3 c1-4 c1-o c1-b c1-4o c1-c c1-55 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g x-rt"><p style="margin:0"><span>Brothers Larry and Kerry Siemsen opened the doors of Old Dixie Seafood in September of 1996. 26&nbsp;years later, this family business had thrived with loyal clientele, friendly customer service, and most importantly, fresh and delicious seafood!<br>
&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div data-ux="GridCell" class="x-el x-el-div c1-1 c1-2 c1-8g c1-o c1-8p c1-8q c1-2y c1-34 c1-8r c1-5b c1-8s c1-b c1-c c1-a4 c1-a5 c1-8t c1-8u c1-8v c1-8w c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><div data-ux="ContentCard" index="2" id="909aad8f-5226-4823-956b-d119519364ad" class="x-el x-el-div x-el c1-1 c1-2 c1-n c1-p c1-s c1-q c1-74 c1-r c1-4 c1-8x c1-8y c1-8z c1-b c1-c c1-90 c1-91 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g c1-1 c1-2 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><div data-ux="ContentCardWrapperImage" class="x-el x-el-div c1-1 c1-2 c1-2e c1-39 c1-3a c1-74 c1-4 c1-92 c1-93 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><picture data-lazyimg="true" class="x-el x-el-picture c1-1 c1-2 c1-4 c1-5t c1-74 c1-94 c1-26 c1-b c1-c c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"><source media="(max-width: 450px)" srcset="https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg/:/cr=t:16.67%25,l:0%25,w:100%25,h:66.67%25/rs=w:403,h:202,cg:true, //img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg/:/cr=t:16.67%25,  isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg 3x"/><source media="(min-width: 451px)" srcset="https://img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg/:/cr=t:16.67%25,l:0%25,w:100%25,h:66.67%25/rs=w:600,h:300,cg:true, //img1.wsimg.com/isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg/:/cr=t:16.67%25,  isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg 3x"/><img data-ux="Image" src="isteam/ip/8b26da3d-75e6-4714-b195-f3246c40c561/7fd9e9cc-b983-4ee4-a945-38d2351dc58d.jpg" data-aid="ABOUT_IMAGE_RENDERED2" class="x-el x-el-img c1-1 c1-2 c1-4 c1-2y c1-39 c1-3a c1-22 c1-24 c1-3b c1-95 c1-b c1-c c1-96 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g"/></picture></div><h4 role="heading" aria-level="4" data-ux="ContentCardHeading" data-aid="ABOUT_HEADLINE_RENDERED2" data-typography="HeadingDelta" class="x-el x-el-h4 c1-1 c1-2 c1-2r c1-2a c1-97 c1-25 c1-23 c1-22 c1-24 c1-b c1-40 c1-6n c1-55 c1-6q c1-6s c1-6t c1-6u">PRODUCTS YOU WILL LOVE</h4><div data-ux="ContentCardText" data-aid="ABOUT_DESCRIPTION_RENDERED2" data-typography="BodyAlpha" class="x-el c1-1 c1-2 c1-2r c1-2a c1-5p c1-22 c1-24 c1-7d c1-98 c1-99 c1-9a c1-9b c1-9c c1-9d c1-9e c1-9f c1-9g c1-9h c1-9i c1-9j c1-9k c1-9l c1-9m c1-9n c1-9o c1-9p c1-9q c1-9r c1-9s c1-9t c1-9u c1-9v c1-9w c1-9x c1-9y c1-9z c1-a0 c1-a1 c1-a2 c1-a3 c1-4 c1-o c1-b c1-4o c1-c c1-55 c1-d c1-e c1-f c1-g x-rt"><p style="margin:0"><span>Fresh and locally caught fish<br>
Homemade salads&nbsp;<br>
Selection of specialty wines, both reds and whites<br>
Our WORLD FAMOUS SMOKED WAHOO&nbsp;SPREAD!! We guarantee you'll love it.<br>
